{"tid":782633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用左一排face id真係頂唔撚順要買返部iphone 8+","createTime":"2018-08-17T01:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T01:09:35.000Z","uid":196751,"like":711,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7a218318e931b764be9dce395fd63d2a119c64","tid":782633,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"趁尾門買返部8+先<br />\n利申左先:<br />\n我係用左半年8+之後因為公司出機比每個同事<br />\n咁我就賣左部8+用公司部x,用左一排face id真係覺得好撚難頂<br />\n<br />\n以前用touch id開緊會都可以偷偷地玩電話,只要放隻手指埋去就unlock<br />\n依加下下都要直接望住部電話先解到<br />\n<br />\n另一個on9係部電話一定要由上而下咁擺先解到<br />\n反轉係認唔撚到你架,touch id就360到解到<br />\n<br />\n最on9係一定要打開晒對眼先unlock到<br />\n有時訓訓下有個msg想覆,對眼一定要開晒先認到<br />\n都算啦,趴係到訓個枕頭遮住少少都解唔到<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母,正垃圾"},{"pid":"399066b959991c7ec524950af24cee33a3d85fd0","tid":782633,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0f3554be5eac92457d6ce076a0c3c410f0475e","tid":782633,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e8c255569f64872e7624d4a6674741767122c0","tid":782633,"uid":196751,"like":62,"dislike":9,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"不服來辨,唔洗偷偷負評"},{"pid":"1e000ad98f87af8f21338337a3810490938160c9","tid":782633,"uid":85564,"like":351,"dislike":6,"score":345,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"同意 指紋解鎖好撚方便"},{"pid":"5dd30a6a430ff116ae9ca0c0d83b15507a58f362","tid":782633,"uid":125516,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8+用家"},{"pid":"73fdc073ef2a2c1792f2849dffc4a05b9eed4ebd","tid":782633,"uid":4448,"like":100,"dislike":6,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"同意 ipho